Array Comparison

array_comp.Rd

Assigning values from a sample to array_inci_comp

Usage

array_comp(
  ana,
  array_comp = NA,
  comp,
  pr_sample,
  topic = topic,
  group,
  crilb = lb,
  criub = ub,
  array_ana = NA
)

Arguments

ana

Type of analysis incidence proportions or rates

array_comp

The array setup for comparisons

comp

"Risk Diff" or "Risk Ratio"

pr_sample

posterior sample for difference or ratio

topic

Variable to be analyzed

group

The current comparison group

crilb

Cri lower bound

criub

Cri upper bound

array_ana

Setup for analyzed array
